The Killer Feature

Automatic Order Reconciliation

Right now, companies constantly fight over:
	•	wrong quantities
	•	wrong prices
	•	wrong SKUs
	•	missing shipments
	•	invoice mismatches

This happens because every company has different data.

Example:

Customer PO:

SKU A
Qty: 500
Price: $12

Distributor system:

SKU A
Qty: 450
Price: $12

Manufacturer system:

SKU A
Qty: 500
Price: $13

Now everyone argues over email.

This wastes massive amounts of time.

⸻

What Your AI Does

Your platform compares all versions of an order across companies.

Then it detects mismatches instantly.

Example:

Order #28492

Customer requested: 500 units
Distributor confirmed: 450 units
Invoice issued: 500 units

Conflict detected.

The AI proposes a resolution.

Suggested resolution:

Ship remaining 50 units next week
or
Adjust invoice to 450


